OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,FTottenham have condemned the "vile,
OL,7,Fdehumanising racism" aimed at defender
OL,8,FKevin Danso following Saturday's 2-2
OL,9,Fdraw with Brighton.
OL,11,FDanso was at fault for Georginio
OL,12,FRutter's stoppage-time equaliser,
OL,13,Fwhich left Spurs languishing in the
OL,14,Frelegation zone.
OL,16,FThe club say they have reported racist
OL,17,Fabuse towards the Austria centre-back
OL,18,Fon social media to the police.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
