PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776665107
OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,F"Since yesterday's fixture against
OL,7,FBrighton, which took place during the
OL,8,FPremier League's No Room For Racism
OL,9,Fweekend, Kevin Danso has been, and
OL,10,Fcontinues to be, subject to
OL,11,Fsignificant and abhorrent racist abuse
OL,12,Fon social media," Spurs said in a club
OL,13,Fstatement.
OL,15,F"We have heard and seen vile,
OL,16,Fdehumanising racism. Behaviour that is
OL,17,Fwithout doubt a criminal offence. It
OL,18,Fwill not be tolerated.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@QO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776665107
OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,F"The club is taking immediate action.
OL,7,FWe are reporting all identified
OL,8,Fcontent to the Metropolitan Police and
OL,9,Fto the appropriate authorities in the
OL,10,Fcountry where perpetrators reside, as
OL,11,Fwell as to relevant social media
OL,12,Fplatforms.
OL,14,F"We will push for the strongest
OL,15,Fpossible action against each and every
OL,16,Fperson we identify.
OL,18,F"Kevin has our complete and
OL,19,Funconditional support as a player and
OL,20,Fas a person. No one at this club will
OL,21,Fever stand alone in the face of this.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
