OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,FDanso posted on Instagram on Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning: "Not the result we needed
OL,8,Fyesterday. We gave everything, we
OL,9,Flearn and we move.
OL,11,F"I've also seen the comments. The
OL,12,Fracist abuse has no place in this game
OL,13,For anywhere. But it doesn't define me,
OL,14,Fand it won't distract me from what is
OL,15,Fimportant. I know who I am, what I
OL,16,Fstand for, and why I play.
OL,26,@oD@JOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
