PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776665107
OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,F"Now it's about staying focused,
OL,7,Fworking harder, and coming back
OL,8,Fstronger for the next games. We keep
OL,9,Fpushing, we keep believing, and we
OL,10,Fgive our all every single time we step
OL,11,Fon that pitch.
OL,13,F"Stronger. Together. On to the next."
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUuD@eO]
