OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,FThe Premier League issued a statement
OL,7,Fon X in support of Danso, warning that
OL,8,F"any individuals identified and found
OL,9,Fguilty of discrimination will face the
OL,10,Fstrongest possible consequences,
OL,11,Fincluding club bans and legal
OL,12,Fprosecution".
OL,14,FThe statement added: "Discriminatory
OL,15,Fabuse has absolutely no place in
OL,16,Ffootball or wider society. Anybody who
OL,17,Fchooses to abuse others is not welcome
OL,18,Fin our game and they are not a true
OL,19,Ffan.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@LO]vD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
