OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776665107
OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,F"It is clear that more needs to be
OL,7,Fdone to address this issue and we will
OL,8,Fwork alongside clubs, football bodies,
OL,9,Flaw enforcement and social media
OL,10,Fcompanies to ensure this remains a
OL,11,Fpriority for all."
OL,13,FAnti-discrimination charity Kick It
OL,14,FOut said in a statement: "We stand
OL,15,Fwith Kevin Danso and all players who
OL,16,Fare calling out this vile abuse. It
OL,17,Ftakes huge courage and Kevin's
OL,18,Fresponse is incredibly powerful.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@RO]vD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
