OL,3,CTottenham report 'abhorrent racist
OL,4,Cabuse' of Kevin Danso to police
OL,6,F"Reports of discrimination sent to
OL,7,FKick It Out ` whether in the
OL,8,Fprofessional game, grassroots or
OL,9,Fonline ` continue to rise this season,
OL,10,Fbut we will meet that with the same
OL,11,Fforce."
